# FEATURES

Authentication: Login/register with JWT

Products

  List products with name, price, image, category, stock.

  Filter by category.

  Search by keyword.

  Sort by price.

Cart

  Add/remove/update product quantity.

Checkout

  Creates an order.

  Rejects if stock is insufficient.

Orders

View list of past orders linked to the logged-in user.

# FUTURE ADD-ONS

Pagination
  For product and order lists, to handle many items efficiently.

Persistent Cart
  Save cart data for logged-in users in the database

Error Handling & Validation
  Improve API responses and input validation.

UI Enhancements
  Better styling, responsive design, and loading states.
